OL,7,FA "risk-taking" former doctor who
OL,8,Fharmed dozens of women by performing
OL,9,Funconsented surgeries went virtually
OL,10,Funchecked by hospital bosses.
OL,12,FHundreds of women were under the care
OL,13,Fof ex-consultant Daniel Hay, aged 60,
OL,14,Fwhen he worked for the University
OL,15,FHospitals of Derby and Burton NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust (UHDB) before he
OL,17,Fretired in 2020 on health grounds.
