OL,7,FA report, which was published on
OL,8,FWednesday, into the care received by
OL,9,FMr Hay's patients at Royal Derby
OL,10,FHospital between 2015 and 2018 found
OL,11,Fthat "severe physical harm" was
OL,12,Fsuffered by two patients.
OL,14,FOn the publication of the report, the
OL,15,Ftrust said it has expressed "deepest
OL,16,Fapologies" to the women who received
OL,17,Fcare from Mr Hay that was "far below
OL,18,Fthe standards we expect".
