OL,7,FThe panel reviewed the cases of 325
OL,8,Fpatients about their experiences with
OL,9,FMr Hay, while 58 women had already
OL,10,Fbeen reviewed in 2019.
OL,12,FThe report concluded that Mr Hay
OL,13,F"lacked clinical judgment", adding:
OL,14,F"He took shortcuts in his clinical
OL,15,Fassessment of patients and over time
OL,16,Fhe showed an increasing willingness to
OL,17,Ftake risks.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@ZO]vD@AOU
