OL,4,Cshortcuts 'contributed to severe
OL,5,Cphysical harm'
OL,7,F"He sometimes had a manner that was
OL,8,Foff-putting, saying little to patients
OL,9,Fduring consultations and failing to
OL,10,Fexplain his course of action in an
OL,11,Funderstandable manner."
OL,13,FSome of the shortcuts by Mr Hay
OL,14,Fincluded not taking full patient
OL,15,Fhistories and not requesting pre-
OL,16,Foperation scans, the report said.
