OL,7,FThe report added: "The panel has
OL,8,Fconducted further analysis of 40
OL,9,Fpatients and found two incidents of
OL,10,Fsevere physical harm, together with
OL,11,Fthree of moderate physical harm, all
OL,12,Fpreviously unrecognised."
OL,14,FIt added that Mr Hay's paperwork was
OL,15,F"not of an acceptable standard", he
OL,16,Fdid not always point out the risks and
OL,17,Fbenefits of procedures which
OL,18,F"unsettled and disturbed" some
OL,19,Fpatients, and consent processes were
OL,20,F"inadequate or late" in many cases.
