OL,7,FThe report, commissioned by the
OL,8,FGynaecology Review Steering Group,
OL,9,Fwhich included representations from
OL,10,FNHS England, UHDB, and the Derby and
OL,11,FDerbyshire Clinical Commissioning
OL,12,FGroup, said that the mental health of
OL,13,Fmany patients had been "adversely
OL,14,Faffected" by Mr Hay's practice.
OL,16,FIt said "the support of colleagues and
OL,17,Fgood fortune prevented further harm
OL,18,Fbeing caused".
