OL,7,FRecommendations were made to the
OL,8,Ftrust, including that consultants
OL,9,Fshould not work in isolation at
OL,10,Fclinics and measures should be put in
OL,11,Fplace to identify poorly performing
OL,12,Fclinicians.
OL,14,FThe trust has also recommended the
OL,15,Finvestigation is expanded to between
OL,16,F2012 and 2015, focusing on major and
OL,17,Fintermediate gynaecology surgery cases.
