OL,7,FThese issues include women having
OL,8,Fhysterectomies who either did not want
OL,9,Fthem, did not know they were having
OL,10,Fthem or did not know alternative, less-
OL,11,Finvasive options were available.
OL,13,FThis led to women who wanted to start
OL,14,Ffamilies and who were still able to do
OL,15,Fso having that opportunity taken away
OL,16,Ffrom them unnecessarily and without
OL,17,Fconsent, leading to ongoing mental
OL,18,Fhealth issues, which have seen them
OL,19,Flose relationships and jobs.
