OL,7,FDr Gis Robinson, executive chief
OL,8,Fmedical officer for the trust, said:
OL,9,F"We want to reiterate our unreserved
OL,10,Fapologies to the women who received
OL,11,Fcare from Mr Hay that was far below
OL,12,Fthe standards expected.
OL,14,F"Following the report we made
OL,15,Fimportant changes, with clearer
OL,16,Fconsent procedures and enhanced
OL,17,Fclinical oversight so any issues with
OL,18,Fcare can be identified more quickly,
OL,19,Fand improved post-procedure reviews
OL,20,Ffor women.
